data.description: Welcome to your new home! Charming, open floor plan home with two living spaces downstairs as well as large loft upstairs. Downstairs, there is a large kitchen that opens to the dining and family room to make room for perfect family time while preparing meals or entertaining. The laundry room and half bath are also downstairs just off of the kitchen.  Heading upstairs, you have a large loft perfect for a kid's playroom, an office area or a workout area. The master bedroom along with three spacious bedrooms are located on this floor as well. The hall bath is spacious as well. The backyard is large and lined with great shade trees and a large shed perfect for storage or project space. On the west side of the backyard, their is potential trailer parking with a double wide gate already installed. The large covered patio in the backyard provides space to entertain during the evenings or weekends.  New HVAC system and ductwork done in the last 12 months. This wonderful home is nestled in a well maintained, quite neighborhood. Call your realtor today for your private showing.
